What you need to know:  Dr Ruto enjoys a cult-like following and his passionate supporters believe his boss Kenyatta has badly mistreated him despite his role in propelling the Jubilee team to power in 2013.This time round, he has galvanised the Kenya Kwanza Alliance and seems to be closing in on claiming the entire Rift Valley.Mr Ruto has demonstrated the ability to withstand pressure. When his trusted followers were hounded out of every office after the “handshake”, he was left with a narrow road to manoeuvre.